			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "reaction"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> the slyxi angler is being hit by a critical hit and is conscious of the attacker</p><hr /><p> The light bulb of the slyxi shines towards the creature's face, who must attempt at a @Check[reflex|dc:18|traits:visual] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> the creature is unaffected.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TkIyaNPgTZFBCCuh]{Dazzled} until the start of its next turn.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> the creature is dazzled for 1 minute and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.XgEqL1kFApUbl5Z2]{Blinded} for 1 round.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> the creature is blinded for 1 minute and dazzled for 2 minuted.</p>",
